text: Kayden Kross (born 1985) is an American pornographic actress and director. She is a member of the AVN and XRCO Halls of Fame. Kross has acted in the FX's comedy series The League, the G4 reality series The Block, and Family Jewels. She was named Penthouse Pet of the Month for September 2008.
